WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Open Centre Third Scout and you will be on the 'Database' tab.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Select a session using the check boxes on the left hand side of the table.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
You can use the 'Delete' or 'Load' buttons when one or more sessions are selected using the check boxes.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Use the table header to search and filter for session by competition, round or team name.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:32.000
Select a session and click 'Load' to import that sessions video and data into the 'Scout' tab.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:38.000
There are two templates that you can choose from the dropdown select to load data - 'live' or 'video'. 

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:46.000
The 'video' template loads data that has been collected post-match and will usually be the only data availalbe for opposition matches. 
